articles.author: Deutsche Welle
articles.title: EU blocks Booking takeover of Swedish online travel rival - DW (English)
articles.description: The European Commission said it prevented the €1.63 ($1.8 billion) deal in order to protect consumers. Booking owns Booking.com, Kayak and other websites, while eTraveli's offerings include Gotogate and MyTrip.
articles.content:
The European Commission blocked US travel giant Booking from acquiring its Swedish rival eTraveli on Monday.
Booking commands a 60% market share for online travel agencies in Europe, the Commission … [+1212 chars]
